== 防灾措施、影响和善后 ==
[[File:1932_Freeport_hurricane_rainfall_totals.png|thumb]]

面对风暴来袭，弗里波特有150辆车撤离，船只沿[[布拉索斯河|布拉索斯河]]尽量朝内陆转移<ref name="stormthreatens">{{cite news | title = Storm Threatens Gulf Coast | newspaper = The Kingsport Times | date = 1932-08-13 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | location = [[休斯敦|Houston]], Texas}}</ref>。[[加尔维斯顿县|加尔维斯顿县]]的[[卡普伦_(德克萨斯州)|卡普伦]]（{{lang|en|Caplen}}）和[[吉尔克里斯特_(德克萨斯州)|吉尔克里斯特]]（{{lang|en|Gilchrist}}）也有100户居民疏散。驻扎在[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]][[帕拉西奥斯_(德克萨斯州)|帕拉西奥斯]]（{{lang|en|Palacios}}）的[[德克萨斯国民警卫队|德克萨斯国民警卫队]]第38师收到飓风来袭警报。<ref name="Texas Hurricanes">{{cite book | title = Texas Hurricane History | archivedate = 2016-12-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161201044253/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | format = PDF | publisher = [[美国国家气象局|United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service]] | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | last1 = Roth | first1 = David M | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center }}</ref>

受风暴影响，德克萨斯州沿海及内陆地区普降暴雨，有四处地点的24小时降雨量创下8月新纪录，并以安格尔顿（{{lang|en|Angleton}}）最高，8月13日测得252毫米雨量，该市还因[[泵水站|泵水站]]被毁面临缺水<ref name="bdgaug15">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Vents Fury; 23 Known Dead; Aid Sought | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=g0gyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=A-MFAAAAIBAJ&pg=813,3144577&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | newspaper = Berkeley Daily Gazette | date = 1932-08-15 | last = Jones | first = Stuart E. | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press]] | location = Houston, Texas | pages = 1, 7 | archive-date = 2021-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210618075629/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=g0gyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=A-MFAAAAIBAJ&pg=813%2C3144577&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。气旋残留又在[[俄克拉何马州|俄克拉何马州]]产生高达300毫米雨量<ref name="Texas Hurricanes" />。[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]在[[圣路易斯水道|圣路易斯水道]]（{{lang|en|San Luis Pass}}）附近救回四艘船的乘客<ref name="stormthreatens" />。[[霍顿县_(德克萨斯州)|霍顿县]]县城[[霍顿_(德克萨斯州)|霍顿]]（{{lang|en|Wharton}}）有800只鸟在暴雨中失踪<ref name="Texas Hurricanes" />。[[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]部分建筑的屋顶被狂风掀开，还有许多窗户破损。[[加尔维斯敦堤道|加尔维斯敦堤道]]（{{lang|en|Galveston Causeway}}）被暴雨淹没，致使[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]同大陆的交通中断。<ref name="stormthreatens" />另外，还有多条公路被倒塌的树木阻塞<ref name="semizzoumagazine">{{cite news | title = 22 Known Dead as Hurricane Sweeps Texas | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=X21FAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Q8cMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3576,5209249&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | newspaper = Southeast Missourian | date = 1932-08-15 | agency = Associated Press | location = Houston, Texas | archive-date = 2021-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210618081307/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=X21FAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Q8cMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3576%2C5209249&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。加尔维斯敦的通讯和供电线路也因风暴受损，导致部分地区停电<ref name="spokane17dead">{{cite news | title = Seventeen Dead After Hurricane | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OtFXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3_QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3716,2856993&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | date = 1932-08-15 | agency = Associated Press | location = Houston, Texas | archive-date = 2021-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210618075652/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OtFXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3_QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3716%2C2856993&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。此外，[[圣安东尼奥_(德克萨斯州)|圣安东尼奥]]也有通讯线缆受损<ref name="stormthreatens" />。

[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]的[[威廉·佩特斯·霍比机场|威廉·佩特斯·霍比机场]]有一个[[飞机库|飞机库]]坍塌，11架飞机受损，经济损失约为25万美元<ref name="bdgaug15" />。[[赫尔曼公园|赫尔曼公园]]（{{lang|en|Hermann Park}}）也受到飓风影响，掉落的树枝将篱笆砸破，九只[[家山羊|山羊]]在园内自由走动<ref name="chron1932recap">{{cite web | title = Let’s hope history doesn’t repeat itself: The 1932 hurricane | url = http://blog.chron.com/sciguy/2009/07/lets-hope-history-doesnt-repeat-itself-the-1932-hurricane/ | archivedate = 2016-08-18 | deadurl = no | publisher = The Houston Chronicle | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818150832/http://blog.chron.com/sciguy/2009/07/lets-hope-history-doesnt-repeat-itself-the-1932-hurricane/ | date = 2012-07-25 | last = Berger | first = Eric }}</ref>。风暴期间，拉姆齐州立监狱突然倒塌，35名犯人逃离，之后只有八人返回，另外27人不知所踪<ref name="prisonersloose">{{cite news | title = Ordered to Run, Prisoners Do It | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=PNFXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3_QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4469,3239287&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | date = 1932-08-17 | agency = Associated Press | location = [[亨茨维尔_(德克萨斯州)|Huntsville, Texas]] | archive-date = 2021-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210618084418/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=PNFXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3_QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4469%2C3239287&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。

风暴过去后，[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]向灾区运送补给物资，并申请一万美元用于救灾<ref name="lewiston32deaths">{{cite news | title = Texas Hurricane Death Toll Now 32 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2IApAAAAIBAJ&sjid=gmYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2714,3322737&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | newspaper = The Daily Sun | date = 1932-08-16 | agency = Associated Press | location = Houston, Texas | archive-date = 2021-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210618075715/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2IApAAAAIBAJ&sjid=gmYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2714%2C3322737&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。另外多个地方救灾组织也向灾区提供物资<ref name="hurricanerelief">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Relief Work Is Pressed | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=yNMrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=i4QFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4792,3474106&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-16 | newspaper = The Daily Record | date = 1932-08-17 | agency = Associated Press | location = Houston, Texas | archive-date = 2021-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210618075734/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=yNMrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=i4QFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4792%2C3474106&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。估计整场飓风单对农作物就造成价值200万美元的损失，其中又以水稻和棉花为主<ref name="lewiston32deaths" />。另有报导认为风暴共夺走40条人命，损失数额约750万美元<ref name="Texas Hurricanes" />。

